      "updated": 1774770901458,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "data object ownership\n1. the object's initial owner of  is who created it\n2. Owner privileges are easily inherited down the hierarchy by granting the right to itself\n3. Objects you don't own won't be visible to you\n\nSecurable Object\n1. data objects: data\n2. non-data objects: assets",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "data object ownership\n1. the object's initial owner of  is who created it\n2. Owner privileges are easily inherited down the hierarchy by granting the right to itself\n3. Objects you don't own won't be visible to you\n\nSecurable Object\n1. data objects: data\n2. non-data objects: assets",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
